OL,3,CNo inquest to take place into death of
OL,4,Cboy, 12, at SnowDome
OL,6,FThere will not be a full inquest into
OL,7,Fthe death of 12-year-old boy who died
OL,8,Fin a collision on a ski slope at the
OL,9,FTamworth SnowDome, a coroner has ruled.
OL,11,FLouis Watkiss, from Sutton Coldfield,
OL,12,Fwas at a toboganning party to
OL,13,Fcelebrate the birthday of a friend
OL,14,Fwhen his toboggan was in collision
OL,15,Fwith a staff member.
