OL,3,CNo inquest to take place into death of
OL,4,Cboy, 12, at SnowDome
OL,6,FAt a hearing at Stafford Coroner's
OL,7,FCourt, coroner Fiona Gingell said on
OL,8,FFriday after reading submissions from
OL,9,Fboth sides that she did not determine
OL,10,Fthere was sufficient reason to hold a
OL,11,Fcoronial investigation.
OL,13,FShe said the previous criminal
OL,14,Finvestigation had already provided a
OL,15,Fclear and factual picture of the
OL,16,Ftragedy.
