OL,3,CNo inquest to take place into death of
OL,4,Cboy, 12, at SnowDome
OL,6,FLouis' parents Natalie and Chris
OL,7,FWatkiss had argued in written
OL,8,Fsubmissions that they believed there
OL,9,Fhad been missed opportunities for
OL,10,Fmedical intervention following the
OL,11,Faccident which they said could have
OL,12,Fmeant their son's injuries were
OL,13,Fsurvivable. They also mentioned a
OL,14,Fdelayed emergency response.
