OL,3,CNo inquest to take place into death of
OL,4,Cboy, 12, at SnowDome
OL,6,FIn their written submission, the
OL,7,FSnowDome had said they did not think
OL,8,Fthere was sufficient reason to
OL,9,Fcontinue with a coronial investigation
OL,10,Fand that if one did go ahead, it
OL,11,Fshouldn't duplicate things heard in
OL,12,Fcourt already.
OL,14,FMs Gingell said she had "taken time to
OL,15,Fconsider and reflect on all
OL,16,Fsubmissions."
OL,18,FShe adds: "Is the emergency response
OL,19,Frelevant? And whether Louis' injuries
OL,20,Fcould have been survivable?"
