OL,3,CNo inquest to take place into death of
OL,4,Cboy, 12, at SnowDome
OL,6,FBut she said CPR had been given to
OL,7,FLouis, that the pathologist had raised
OL,8,Fno concerns regarding the emergency
OL,9,Fresponse and that "Louis' injuries
OL,10,Fwere sadly unsurvivable."
OL,12,FIn February, the SnowDome was fined
OL,13,Fmore than #100,000 after pleading
OL,14,Fguilty to breaching health and safety
OL,15,Fregulations over Louis' death.
OL,17,FAfter the ruling Louis' grandfather
OL,18,Faddressed the SnowDome saying: "You
OL,19,Fchose your legal representative
OL,20,Fexcellently"
